IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: TO PROVIDE FREE LEGAL REPRESENTATION TO ELIGIBLE LOWINCOME DISABLED AND SENIOR RESIDENTS OF BERGEN HUDSON AND PASSAIC COUNTIES
IRS990.MissionDesc: TO PROVIDE FREE LEGAL REPRESENTATION TO ELIGIBLE LOW-INCOME, DISABLED AND SENIOR RESIDENTS OF BERGEN, HUDSON AND PASSAIC COUNTIES IN NEW JERSEY.
IRS990.Desc: IN THE YEAR ENDING JUNE 30, 2023, NNJLS PROVIDED DIRECT LEGAL ASSISTANCE TO OVER 11,410 PERSONS IN THE AREA OF HOUSING, CONSUMER ISSUES, FAMILY ISSUES AND PUBLIC BENEFIT LAW MATTERS. NNJLS ALSO PROVIDED COMMUNITY-BASED LEGAL EDUCATION TO OVER 3,600 LOW INCOME RESIDENTS OF BERGEN, HUDSON AND PASSAIC COUNTIES.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: NORTHEAST NEW JERSEY LEGAL SERVICES CORP. IS IN CUSTODY OF AN ATTORNEY
TRUST ACCOUNT, AS REQURED BY THE NEW JERSEY COURT RULE 1:21 (C) (A)
FOR KEEPING CLIENT PROPERTY MONEY SEPARATE DURING THE REPRESENTATION
OF A CLIENT.
NORTHEAST NEW JEREY LEGAL SERVICES CORP. IS EXEMPT FROM FEDERAL INCOME
TAX UNDER SECTION 501(C)(3) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE AND THEREFORE
HAS MADE NO PROVISION FOR FEDERAL OR STATE INCOME TAX IN THE ACCOMPANYING
FINANCIAL STATEMENTS. IN ADDITION, NNJLS HAS BEEN DETERMINED BY THE
INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE NOT TO BE "PRIVATE FOUNDATION" WITHIN THE MEANING
OF SECTION 509(A)(1) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE.
OTHER SIGNIFICANT TAX POSITION INCLUDE ITS DETERMINATION OF WHETHER ANY
AMOUNTS ARE SUBJECT TO UNRELATED BUSINESS INCOME TAX ("UBIT"). MANAGEMENT
HAS DETERMINED THAT NNJLS HAD NO ACTIVITIES SUBJECT TO UBIT IN THE YEARS
ENDED JUNE 30, 2023 OR 2022. ALL SIGNIFICANT TAX POSITION HAVE BEEN
